javax.microedition.lcdui

Class CwaActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • Activity
      • javax.microedition.lcdui.CwaActivity
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    PetKing5

    public class CwaActivity
extends Activity
    CwaActivity is an Android Activity that manages the lifecycle and UI of the application. It includes methods for managing the canvas, handling memory, and interacting with the MIDletManager. This class also provides functionality for setting full-screen mode and handling key events.
